# Example DVC remote configuration (copy into .dvc/config after `dvc init`)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Local remote (good default for getting started):
#   dvc remote add -d localremote /path/to/shared/storage
#
# S3:
#   dvc remote add -d s3remote s3://your-bucket/demand-forecasting
#   dvc remote modify s3remote region us-east-1
#
# GCS:
#   dvc remote add -d gcsremote gs://your-bucket/demand-forecasting
